Motorists are warned of ongoing protests around the Jika Joe informal settlement areas in Pietermaritzburg on Monday morning. Motorists are urged to steer clear of the area as unconfirmed reports have been received of protesters burning tyres on all four sides of the informal settlements. Masukwana Street (formerly known as East Street) and Loop Street are no go areas as the streets have been blockaded with burning tyres, according to reports. *This is a developing story